    "description_long": "This is a tall, rectangular floor-standing stereo speaker system with a rich, reddish-brown wood veneer exterior. The front face features three large, circular speaker drivers arranged vertically, with a smaller tweeter at the top, all set within black mounting frames. The sides and back are smooth and unadorned, showcasing the natural wood grain pattern. The base is slightly flared, providing stability and a subtle decorative touch. The speaker's design is modern yet classic, suitable for high-fidelity audio in home or public urban environments. No visible controls, ports, or branding are present on the exterior surfaces.",
